#. type: Plain text
#: src/basic.texi:414
msgid "The @kbd{@key{DEL}} (@code{delete-backward-char}) command removes the character before point, moving the cursor and the characters after it backwards.  If point was at the beginning of a line, this deletes the preceding newline, joining this line to the previous one."
msgstr "@kbd{@key{DEL}} (@code{delete-backward-char}) 命令会在游标前移除字符，然后移动光标和字符。 如果游标在一行的开头，则删除前面的换行符，并将此行与前一行连接起来。"

#. type: Plain text
#: src/basic.texi:417
msgid "If, however, the region is active, @kbd{@key{DEL}} instead deletes the text in the region.  @xref{Mark}, for a description of the region."
msgstr "但是，如果选区处于激活状态，则@kbd{@key{DEL}} 删除选区内的文本。@xref{标记}，以获取选区的描述。"

#. type: Plain text
#: src/basic.texi:423
msgid "On most keyboards, @key{DEL} is labeled @key{BACKSPACE}, but we refer to it as @key{DEL} in this manual.  (Do not confuse @key{DEL} with the @key{Delete} key; we will discuss @key{Delete} momentarily.)  On some text terminals, Emacs may not recognize the @key{DEL} key properly.  @xref{DEL Does Not Delete}, if you encounter this problem."
msgstr "在大多数键盘上，@key{DEL} 被标记为@key{BACKSPACE}, 但在本手册中我们将其称为@key{DEL} 。 (不要混淆@key{DEL} 和 @key{Delete} 键；我们会在稍后讨论@key{Delete} 键。) 在一些文本终端上，Emacs 可能无法正确识别@key{DEL} 键。如果您遇到这个问题，请参考@xref{DEL Does Not Delete}。"

#. type: Plain text
#: src/basic.texi:429
msgid "The @key{Delete} (@code{delete-forward-char}) command deletes in the opposite direction: it deletes the character after point, i.e., the character under the cursor.  If point was at the end of a line, this joins the following line onto this one.  Like @kbd{@key{DEL}}, it deletes the text in the region if the region is active (@pxref{Mark})."
msgstr "按键命令@key{Delete} (@code{delete-forward-char}) 会删除与按键命令@key{DEL}作用方向相反的内容：它删除光标后的字符，或者说光标下的字符。 如果光标在一行的末尾，就把下面的行连接到这行上。 与@kbd{@key{DEL}}相似，如果区域处于选中状态，则删除选中区域中的文本 (@pxref{Mark})。"

#. type: Plain text
#: src/basic.texi:433
msgid "@kbd{C-d} (@code{delete-char}) deletes the character after point, similar to @key{Delete}, but regardless of whether the region is active."
msgstr "快捷键{C-d}({delete-char}) 删除游标之后的字符，与{Delete} 类似，但与选区是否处于活动状态无关。"

#. type: Plain text
#: src/basic.texi:436
msgid "@xref{Deletion}, for more detailed information about the above deletion commands."
msgstr "有关上述删除命令的详细信息，请参阅@xref{Deletion}。"

#. type: Plain text
#: src/basic.texi:441
msgid "@kbd{C-k} (@code{kill-line}) erases (kills) a line at a time.  If you type @kbd{C-k} at the beginning or middle of a line, it kills all the text up to the end of the line.  If you type @kbd{C-k} at the end of a line, it joins that line with the following line."
